# Ignore everything
**

# -- Keep Readme ---
!**/README.md


# --- Keep R Markdown / Quarto source files ---
!**/*.Rmd
!**/*.qmd
!**/*.Rproj
!**/_site.yml
!**/_quarto.yml

# --- Keep knitted outputs and report-like documents ---
!**/*.html
!**/*.pdf
!**/*.docx

# --- Keep this gitignore file itself ---
!.gitignore

# --- Keep images and style files used in reports ---
!**/*.png
!**/*.jpg
!**/*.jpeg
!**/*.svg
!**/*.css
!**/*.js
!**/*.yml

# --- Ignore cache and temporary render files ---
**/*_cache/
**/cache/
**/*.utf8.md
**/*.knit.md
**/.Rhistory
**/.RData
**/.Rproj.user/
**/.Ruserdata
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
